j warto\u015b\u0107:<\/b> Zamiast jedynie wskazywa\u0107 cen\u0119, poka\u017c, jakie oszcz\u0119dno\u015bci lub korzy\u015bci przyniesie d\u0142ugoterminowe u\u017cytkowanie Twojego produktu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skuteczne promowanie produkt\u00f3w premium wymaga zrozumienia potrzeb Twojej grupy docelowej oraz umiej\u0119tno\u015bci komunikacji warto\u015bci. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce nie ka\u017cdy klient b\u0119dzie zainteresowany premium funkcjami, ale je\u015bli przyci\u0105gniesz odpowiedni\u0105 publiczno\u015b\u0107, Twoje wysi\u0142ki z pewno\u015bci\u0105 si\u0119 op\u0142ac\u0105.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Czy zastanawiasz si\u0119, jak skutecznie promowa\u0107 produkty premium w kategorii Beauty i FMCG?<\/h2>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4329,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4328","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4328"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4328"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4328\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4329"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4328"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubran